{"tid":1795283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［多圖長文正視聽］大家好似唔記得左","createTime":"2019-12-23T18:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T18:52:17.000Z","uid":320138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ea26f8ad042698388e03304de8bdd85b9de74298","tid":1795283,"uid":320138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T18:42:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpoc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=8c32d76f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">在晚星　墜落　徬徨午夜<br />\n迷霧裡　最遠處吹來　號角聲<br />\n捍自由　來齊集這裡　來全力抗對<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇氣　智慧</span>　也永不滅</span><br />\n<br />\n我地而家就係去到徬徨午夜，被失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，被自殺<br />\n義士一個一個咁消失，白色恐怖已經做到出曬面，<br />\n和平集會比班狗搞亂既情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地而家好似乜都做唔到？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母呀</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地6月開始上街，到而家做到一項訴求，屌你但係我地有五大訴求呀，其他四樣呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">撤回義士檢控</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地可以聖誕節出黎做港豬，但係有冇諗過比人收押左既義士，佢地面對既係未知既未來，你重做港豬你對得著佢地咩？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">撤銷義士控罪</span></strong></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">收回暴動定義</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每一個星期有幾多手足比人帶上庭，暴動就直接十年啦，你唔好同我講你唔識啲義士所以唔理佢地，佢地企響最前線，食左幾多橡膠子彈催淚彈，連實彈都食撚埋，換黎既只係比人當係condom?手足絕對唔係condom，一定要逼政府收回暴動定義，換番手足既青春返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">設獨立調查委員會查警暴</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HOciFMy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHOciFMy.jpg&h=c69016c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z97KBj9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz97KBj9.jpg&h=b152ef10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktzduFa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktzduFa.png&h=1e52064b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面冰山一角，你原諒到佢地？呢班連畜生都不如既生物，新屋嶺，721 831 101 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋咁多浮屍、被自殺，監警會你覺得佢地做到野？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">自己人查自己人</span></strong></span>你都信？<br />\n一日唔成立獨立調查委員會，一日唔會有公正既判決，呢班生物只會攞著槍指向我地心口。<span style=\"color: red;\">你係咪想再見到手足既生命繼續消逝？</span><br />\n<br />\n到最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">我要真雙普選呀屌你老母</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好聽啲叫一國兩制，但係而家蚛蝈只係想染紅我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我要既係港人治港，支共你唔撚好插你啲濕尻人入黎搞我地香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地堅持左6個月，流過血流過淚，對抗著呢班支共走狗，點解我地頂到咁耐？因為我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勇氣智慧也永不滅</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地諗著好多唔同既方法，和你飛 和你塞 和你唱 到而家和你shop，我地都知道可以點做先可以向政府施壓，揸著香港個春袋&mdash;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">經濟</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好話要全民勇武，我地要既係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和勇一家</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yJjpBq2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyJjpBq2.jpg&h=106d8dc1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3Rb0SH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3Rb0SH.jpg&h=e6df19c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不割席呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你睇政府日日響電視播叫我地割就知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家頂左6個月，唔差在頂埋佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打支共咁易佢就唔會有咁大塊地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點都好，大家要做到<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">核爆都唔割</span></span>，我地先有機會贏<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">最後</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YdBZ9Ng.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYdBZ9Ng.jpg&h=0c7844c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PLvTuPV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPLvTuPV.jpg&h=a7e9284c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n五毛死開，分化撚死撚開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比我知你地響光復左香港之後扮手足響煲底慶祝我實打到你變殘廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae03ddac6b541e665d174fde5c7d2012084babd","tid":1795283,"uid":320138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T18:50:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b04edc20f6b2a739605d7f20f2861840c774ebc","tid":1795283,"uid":320138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T18:50:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4cc032bedc5881e9f6ebc4e8d5ff1cd9a5abed","tid":1795283,"uid":320138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T18:50:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d598b5d21089339acdff04c901feead69709c31","tid":1795283,"uid":320138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T18:50:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48dc3323fd6a3fe9b4fd26d5e27573dac3937cc","tid":1795283,"uid":320138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T18:52:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}